# Product Ops Maturity Transformations – Large Healthcare & Big 4 Engagements

**Category:** Operating Model Modernization  
**North Star:** Shift from project-based to outcome-driven product leadership.  

**Problem:** Fragmented product processes and lack of empowered teams.  

**Solution:** EDGE framework implementation, Cagan “Transformed” model integration, intake rituals, and cross-team prioritization.  

**Impact:** Accelerated roadmaps and stronger cross-functional trust.  

**Product Edge Alignment:** The origin of all frameworks in this repo.  
**Key Learnings:** Frameworks only deliver value when paired with real behavior change.
